text: Caption Geano Auriemma's Team Geno Cloe Poisson / Hartford Courant Cloe Poisson / Hartford Courant Team Geno: Briana Pulido Cloe Poisson / Hartford Courant Cloe Poisson / Hartford Courant See more galleries UConn announced the results of a fan vote that has led to the rosters for First Night on Oct. 16 at Gampel Pavilion. Geno Auriemma and his players are first in the gallery followed by Kevin Ollie and his team.
